WEBVTT

00:00:58.502 --> 00:01:00.811
My father wears it now in solidarity.

00:01:03.295 --> 00:01:09.318
That night began my formal relationship
with death -- my death --

00:01:09.342 --> 00:01:13.150
and it also began
my long run as a patient.

00:01:13.174 --> 00:01:14.328
It's a good word.

00:01:14.352 --> 00:01:16.079
It means one who suffers.

00:01:16.825 --> 00:01:18.266
So I guess we're all patients.

00:01:19.607 --> 00:01:21.973
Now, the American health care system

00:01:21.997 --> 00:01:25.118
has more than its fair share
of dysfunction --

00:01:25.142 --> 00:01:27.202
to match its brilliance, to be sure.

00:01:27.750 --> 00:01:32.202
I'm a physician now,
a hospice and palliative medicine doc,